but, like, I'm here with

41:20.260 --> 41:22.131
a positive attitude
and a hard work.

41:22.175 --> 41:23.524
My biggest thing is
trying to understand how

41:23.568 --> 41:25.395
did I not meet
your expectations.

41:25.439 --> 41:29.008
I remember at high school,
if I got a unsatisfactory grade

41:29.051 --> 41:31.358
