like, as a chief stew,

41:35.580 --> 41:40.410
if a stewardess or
a bunny came on board,

41:40.454 --> 41:42.238
if they were helpful
and they made issues

41:42.282 --> 41:43.544
that you had before better...

41:43.588 --> 41:44.632
