the end of the charter,

41:44.676 --> 41:46.068
and we'll talk then.

41:46.112 --> 41:47.417
Okay, sure.

41:47.461 --> 41:48.593
-Okay?
-Yeah.

41:48.636 --> 41:50.986
Yeah, I think it
would be quite fair

41:51.030 --> 41:52.553
