at the end of the trip.

41:52.597 --> 41:54.947
Cool.

41:54.990 --> 41:56.688
Should I go continue
doing laundry?

41:56.731 --> 41:59.081
You can take two hours.

41:59.125 --> 42:00.909
-Okay.
-Cool, thank you.

42:00.953 --> 42:02.607
Thank you.

42:06.262 --> 42:08.134
She's right, she did try.

42:08.177 --> 42:09.570
It wasn't like she wasn't
trying or anything like that.

42:09.614 --> 42:12.486
It was just causing
me more stress.

42:12.530 --> 42:14.967
But now we just have
to see where we're at

42:15.010 --> 42:16.229
at the end of the charter.

42:16.272 --> 42:18.710
The situation's so ----ed.

42:18.753 --> 42:20.450
Man, it is gnarly.

42:20.494 --> 42:23.366
