43:14.461 --> 43:16.158
Deck crew, deck crew, Lexi.

43:18.639 --> 43:20.554
<i>Getting a little nervous.</i>

43:20.598 --> 43:24.036
Oh, my God, that's ----ing
crazy-looking out there.

43:24.079 --> 43:25.646
Oh, look at these waves.

43:25.690 --> 43:27.474
I'm scared, I want out
of this place.

43:27.517 --> 43:30.172
Woo-hoo!

43:30.216 --> 43:31.565
Lloyd, Lloyd, Lexi.

43:31.609 --> 43:33.654
